{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/announcements/2016/06/23/updates-and-announcements.html","webpackCompilationHash":"0c5d630095500f933ccd","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Articles by thoughtram","authors":[{"id":"pascal_precht","name":"Pascal Precht","twitter":"PascalPrecht","img":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/445106?s=460&v=4"},{"id":"christoph_burgdorf","name":"Christoph Burgdorf","twitter":"cburgdorf","img":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/521109?s=460&v=4"},{"id":"dominic_elm","name":"Dominic Elm","twitter":"d3lm","img":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/12571019?s=400&v=4"},{"id":"thomas_burleson","name":"Thomas Burleson","twitter":"thomasburleson","img":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/210413?s=400&v=4"},{"id":"elvira_eulitz","name":"Elvira Eulitz","twitter":"ElviraEulitz","img":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/29247040?s=400&v=4"},{"id":"maxim_koretskyi","name":"Maxim Koretskyi","twitter":"maxim_koretskyi","img":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/6124091?s=400&v=4"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"06a1ab28-9ed2-5047-a314-5bab75e4ae95","excerpt":"Today we like to bring you up to date with all the exciting things that we were working on over the last couple of weeks. The search bar Two months ago we…","html":"<p>Today we like to bring you up to date with all the exciting things that we were working on over the last couple of weeks.</p>\n<h2>The search bar</h2>\n<p>Two months ago we rolled out a new design for our blog to make discovering all our different articles a whole lot easier. The feedback we got is overwhelming and we are thrilled to see how many people read and love our blog. Just recently we hit <strong>170k sessions per month</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bdf69be296c7020b96faff51e049ccf0/04132/170k_monthly_sessions.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.61486486486486%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"170k monthly sessions\"\n        title=\"170k monthly sessions\"\n        src=\"/static/bdf69be296c7020b96faff51e049ccf0/8ff1e/170k_monthly_sessions.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bdf69be296c7020b96faff51e049ccf0/9ec3c/170k_monthly_sessions.png 200w,\n/static/bdf69be296c7020b96faff51e049ccf0/c7805/170k_monthly_sessions.png 400w,\n/static/bdf69be296c7020b96faff51e049ccf0/8ff1e/170k_monthly_sessions.png 800w,\n/static/bdf69be296c7020b96faff51e049ccf0/04132/170k_monthly_sessions.png 1184w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>With that in mind we thought it would be nice to make it simpler to search for articles on our blog. Say hello to the new search bar feature which makes finding articles on our blog easier than ever before.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d2fa9ef42a31c0e86c8ffb18b0fc6276/f2201/search-bar.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.387459054749655%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"search bar feature\"\n        title=\"search bar feature\"\n        src=\"/static/d2fa9ef42a31c0e86c8ffb18b0fc6276/8ff1e/search-bar.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d2fa9ef42a31c0e86c8ffb18b0fc6276/9ec3c/search-bar.png 200w,\n/static/d2fa9ef42a31c0e86c8ffb18b0fc6276/c7805/search-bar.png 400w,\n/static/d2fa9ef42a31c0e86c8ffb18b0fc6276/8ff1e/search-bar.png 800w,\n/static/d2fa9ef42a31c0e86c8ffb18b0fc6276/6ff5e/search-bar.png 1200w,\n/static/d2fa9ef42a31c0e86c8ffb18b0fc6276/2f950/search-bar.png 1600w,\n/static/d2fa9ef42a31c0e86c8ffb18b0fc6276/f2201/search-bar.png 2137w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Meet us at thoughtram TV</h2>\n<p>Many of you asked us to share more information about our process to learn and teach Angular, organize workshops, write articles and more. We are listening and are excited to share more of these kind of things with you in our new format thoughtram TV.</p>\n<p>In the first episode of thoughtram TV you’ll get to see parts of an internal review call where we discuss how to improve the setup experience for the attendees of our workshops.</p>\n<p>Don’t forget to subscribe to <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBn1x1RwoQkLmC8UPCNty0Q\">our channel on YouTube</a>!</p>\n<iframe class=\"thtrm-tv\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLMEcDV4jlGhxRBHwNgsP2h5KaEwvSACL0&amp;showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n<h2>Angular 2 Master Class: Helsinki</h2>\n<p>We’re thrilled to announce yet another public <strong>Angular 2 Master Class</strong>. It’s in Helsinki and it’s gonna be epic. The venue for this event is actual an old fortress on an Island. It’s an <strong>UNESCO world heritage site</strong> and will give this event an unforgettable touch. Shout out to Panu from <a href=\"https://www.frantic.com\">frantic</a> who helps us organizing the event and pointed us to this beauty.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/79e8585414621d71465455d06a339588/eba6f/suomenlinna.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.13812154696133%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Suomenlinna\"\n        title=\"Suomenlinna\"\n        src=\"/static/79e8585414621d71465455d06a339588/a296c/suomenlinna.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/79e8585414621d71465455d06a339588/f544b/suomenlinna.jpg 200w,\n/static/79e8585414621d71465455d06a339588/41689/suomenlinna.jpg 400w,\n/static/79e8585414621d71465455d06a339588/a296c/suomenlinna.jpg 800w,\n/static/79e8585414621d71465455d06a339588/c35de/suomenlinna.jpg 1200w,\n/static/79e8585414621d71465455d06a339588/8179c/suomenlinna.jpg 1600w,\n/static/79e8585414621d71465455d06a339588/eba6f/suomenlinna.jpg 1810w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The event takes place <strong>5th and 6th of September 2016</strong> and you can get your ticket right now, right here. Better be quick, there’ll only be 5 early bird tickets for a limited time!</p>\n<iframe  src=\"//eventbrite.de/tickets-external?eid=26144490876&ref=etckt\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"325\" width=\"100%\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" marginheight=\"5\" marginwidth=\"5\" scrolling=\"auto\" allowtransparency=\"true\"></iframe>\n<p>Checkout the <a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.de/e/angular-2-master-class-helsinki-tickets-26144490876\">event page</a> for a more detailed description.</p>","frontmatter":{"author":"christoph_burgdorf",